videos.headline: Missouri QB Cook keeps it himself for 30-yard TD
videos.description: Missouri quarterback Brady Cook keeps it on the read option and takes off for the 30-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri QB Cook keeps it himself for 30-yard TD) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army QB Anderson follows his blockers for 22-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Army's Christian Anderson rolls right and has loads of blockers out in front on his way to a 22-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army QB Anderson follows his blockers for 22-yard rushing TD) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missouri band joined by 'Spot' the dancing robot
videos.description: Missouri's marching band is joined by a dancing robot named "Spot" at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri band joined by 'Spot' the dancing robot) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army's Buchanan absolutely trucks a defender for a TD
videos.description: Army running back Jakobi Buchanan puts a defender on the grass en route to a 10-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army's Buchanan absolutely trucks a defender for a TD) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army takes the lead with a TD on 4th down
videos.description: Army fakes out the whole Missouri defense as quarterback Tyhier Tyler throws it to Brandon Walters for the 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army takes the lead with a TD on 4th down) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missouri has costly turnover in the 4th
videos.description: Missouri running back Dawson Downing gets the ball knocked loose and it's recovered by Army's Andre Carter II.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri has costly turnover in the 4th) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missouri takes the late lead after Cook finds Chism for TD
videos.description: Missouri's Brady Cook ropes a pass to Keke Chism in the back of the end zone for a touchdown and the lead with under two minutes remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri takes the late lead after Cook finds Chism for TD) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army takes down Missouri in back-and-forth ballgame
videos.description: Army and Missouri trade blows throughout the game as the Black Knights prevail on a last-second field goal to win 24-22.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Army takes down Missouri in back-and-forth ballgame) 2021/12/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Army nips Mizzou on last-second FG in Armed Forces Bowl
videos.description: After Missouri scores a touchdown to go ahead with 1:11 left, the Black Knights counter with a 41-yard field goal as time expires to win, 24-22.
